								<wikidot:authorUserId>5869409</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I admit, I'm definitely not very well-versed with most of the crosslinks here, but the base narrative here is still impactful enough to make me feel sympathetic for MacKenzie. The communication logs + notices all show the immense amount of work and stress MacKenzie went through to finally get the machine up and running, only to be destroyed in a single series of events. Her behavior after the incident just seals the sheer amount of despair she's in.</p> <p>+1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
